               <p>ROBERT HARMAN. On the 1st of March, between five and six o'clock in the afternoon, I was in <placeName id="t18300415-295-crimeloc1609">Coventry-street Haymarket</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18300415-295-crimeloc1609" type="placeName" value="Coventry-street Haymarket"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18300415-295-crimeloc1609" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-295-off1607 t18300415-295-crimeloc1609"></join>; I had a handkerchief in my pocket - I did not feel any thing, but a gentleman told me my pocket was picked; I turned, saw the prisoner in his hand, and my handkerchief at his feet.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by MR. HEATON. Q. Is that gentleman here? A. Yes; this is the handkerchief - I had not seen the prisoner before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300415-295-person2490">
                  THOMAS 
                  HOLLINS
               <interp inst="t18300415-295-person2490" type="surname" value="HOLLINS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300415-295-person2490" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300415-295-person2490" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was in the street, and saw the prisoner and other following the gentleman - I watched them, and saw the prisoner pick his pocket; I collared him, and the gentleman turned and took him.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined. Q. Do you swear you saw him take it out of the pocket? A. Yes; the others were behind him - I do not know what became of them.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. This gentleman says there were three of us, but there was only one more beside me; I saw another boy take it - I was going to tell the gentleman, when I was accused of it.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18300415-295-verdict1610" type="verdictDescription">
